    • Constructor Detail

      • PatternCard

        public PatternCard(DiceContainer diceContainer,
                   int id,
                   java.lang.String name,
                   int difficulty,
                   java.lang.String patternCardRepresentation)
        Depending on the patternCardRepresentation, it creates 20 cells. For each char of patternCardRepresentation, it creates a cell with a precise constraint. A cell can't have both a value and a color constraint.
        Parameters:
        diceContainer - dice container
        id - pattern card id
        name - pattern card name
        difficulty - pattern card difficulty
        patternCardRepresentation - pattern card representation, composed of 20 chars where every char corresponds to a cell
